# Project Overview

This is a Snapdrop clone project - a local file sharing web application that allows users to share files between devices on the same network without the need for internet connectivity.

## Key Components

- [server.js](mdc:server.js): Main server application that handles WebSocket connections and file transfers
- [database.js](mdc:database.js): Database operations for managing device information
- [public/](mdc:public): Frontend assets and client-side application
- [uploads/](mdc:uploads): Temporary storage for file transfers

## Main Features

1. Real-time device discovery on local network
2. Direct file transfers between devices
3. Text message sharing
4. Cross-platform compatibility

